{"text": "I'm glad I tried the new path even if I cannot remember anything from the two first routes. I'm glad I didn't put the game into my hidden list because I didn't find anything striking in it. Caine's story is perfect! Topics about bullying and abuses are \"refreshing\" if I can use that word... because so few take the risk to speak about them, moreover in our time.  So yeah, the game is really girly as there is a dress-up game coupled into the Otome, but it's not a brainless one saved only by its arts. It's nicely written even if the choice options are only \"kind\" or \"fierce\" action. The only things that are painfully irritating is the fact you have some difficulties to understand which color you need to use on the pattern of requested clothes, so I'm taking commission only on things I can understand what color it's actually though it's a problem when it's required for the next chapter and you don't know which color you need to buy... urg! I'm still recommending it!", "appid": "939330", "steamid": "profiles/76561198255960253", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "5", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1596196800.0}
