{"text": "This game is PURE GEM! After only one level I was asking myself...where was this game all my life! By far most fun runner game or any game for that matter I have played ina while, if not ever. Runs buttery smooth, colors, action, sounds - everything is top notch. And soundtrack deserves special mentioning - its amazing. Its super addictive, you can go \"naked\" or use things like a partner (that kills enemies, gives you 2x points and many other things). You can customize your character to a point, mostly visualy. 3 different game modes, from time limit one to the ones with fixed enemies locations and spawning obstacles where you go for points high score. Only things I would prefer is more tracks but there are DLC one (which are not a must), but for such an amazing game as this I will gladly buy them all in the future. Its that good. I play with gamepad and it works like a charm, gives you superfast fluid reactions where its only up to you and your reflexes. This is THE BEST runner game by far. If you like Tron and or runner games you just owe it to yourself to buy it. Price is more than fair. Got to admit it, Disney published one heck of a game.", "appid": "392000", "steamid": "profiles/76561198057622074", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "14", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1585224000.0}
