{"text": "I love cheese. No I don't mean a large pizza with extra cheese or a nice gooey grilled cheese sandwich. I mean cheesy, tongue-in-cheek, over-the-top-acting....something that   has in spades.  FMV games take me back to my early days of PC gaming; being the height of video game technology at the time, it seemed that everyone was doing them. To come across new and modern FMV games was like being swaddled in a blanket that was warm and fuzzy, but also old and familiar. I had to jump on this game and see if the style was \"as good\" as I remembered. Contradiction has:  Contradiction needs:  If you're a fan of FMV style games, this isn't a bad title to pick up. Granted, I have yet to see this game go on sale, but if you're looking to support or encourage more devs to revitalize the FMV genre, you could do a lot worse.", "appid": "373390", "steamid": "profiles/76561198006837455", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "30", "votes_funny": "6", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1542974400.0}
