{"text": "After playing this game I regret not buying it sooner.  This game is a tragic story about personal loss and the things we do to deal with those situations. Two siblings, referred to only as Big Brother and Little Brother, are united to find a cure for their father's mysterious ailment. You control both brothers, the right side of the controller controls the younger brother, who is at most times quite helpless but he can slip through bars and help his big brother out on numerous tasks. Then we have the left side of controller that controls the big brother, who can boost his little brother up to higher ledges, he helps his little brother when they are swimming and the strenght allows him to pull heavy levers. While the brothers are on an adventure in this gorgeous world which simply is bursting with personality you will encounter varies \"challenges\" which is the puzzles you have to do along the way. There isn't alot of puzzle solving you have to do and it's pretty easy to figure out what the brothers have to do. The soundtrack is absolutely stunning and powerful, whether you are navigating one of the dream like stages where an older memory comes back to haunt you or wandering through the dark and scary woods. What an amazing journey the game gave me, it's not very lenghty but I promise you that you will enjoy every moment of it.", "appid": "225080", "steamid": "profiles/76561198092310770", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "13", "votes_funny": "21", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1514894400.0}
