{"text": "Before i bought the game, I have received a good feedback on this game. It was on sale, so i had to buy it, and lemme tell you, i have never been so happy before about buying a game for 47 euros. It might be a bit salty for my wallet, but it was worth it. First things first, Customization - I took me an hour to customize my character. The variety of hair styles, appearance, emotions, voice is just huge. For example if you try to make yourself, it will take some time to decide between which lip shape to choose. Second, Landscapes - I just love, LOVE games with some beautiful sceneries. When i play open world games like this i really love to take alot of screenshots, so this is just perfect for me. Third, Story - Story is like one of the important things for me, when i pick up a new game. Since i have played this only for an hour, i can't really tell anything about it yet. So far i have seen some characters, and some action going on at the beginning of the game. Forth, Multiplayer - As much as i have seen other streamers play this game, the monster fights are HARD, so its SUPER handy if you have a friend to play this game with, because its much easier like that. So this is a really good game to pick up, if you are looking for a game to play with your friends as well. Overal - The game is beautiful and full of adventure. The game might have costed 47 euros, but i am so damn positive, that i won't regret the decision of buying it. P.S. Since the game is about fighting monsters, this will be one damn good game to grind, with endless monster fights. Gotta get my game face on ( Í¡â—‰ ÍœÊ– Í¡â—‰)", "appid": "582010", "steamid": "profiles/76561198304891882", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1539345600.0}
