{"text": "PC Building Sim is fantastic. Simple, yet highly entertaining and with an immersive career mode that will make you grind for hours on end to get the best parts. Just like in real life, except you can't really play games with them. But it does let you overclock the crap out of it, benchmark and then brag about how high your 3DMark score is. It's PCMR in a nutshell, except you don't spend thousands of bucks and you can even go a little further than usual and eventually fry an i9 9900k for the sake of getting higher clocks. Not something you'd like to happen with your real CPU, but I bet you wondered how far you could overclock a processor until it dies on you. Wonder no more! It has hundreds of different parts, ranging from fancy cases to RGB fans, allowing for fantastic unique builds that you can only dream of owning. Oh, the wonders of high-end PC hardware! If you love building computers and getting insanely high scores on 3DMark without the need of owning two RTX2080Tis, this game is meant for you. It will definitely keep you busy for at least 40 hours, and the regular updates will always keep your builds updated with the best parts available.  PCBS also makes it clear that yes, money can definitely buy happiness.", "appid": "621060", "steamid": "profiles/76561198103754372", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "22", "votes_funny": "3", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1574856000.0}
