{"text": "A true classic that was part of my childhood! I was able to enjoy several hours of fun, playing with my cousins, uncles, at my grandmother's house who recently left (Rest in peace, my dear), who were all fans of this game. It is really great to be able to enjoy it again at the current moment. It has aged very well, has great gameplay and excellent scenarios, the destruction factor was also well worked out, for me this was the best FlatOut among all of the series. I remember when I enjoyed running and participating in the derby of this game while listening to its soundtracks, a good old nostalgia. It is worth every cent, regardless of whether you are on a promotion or not, I guarantee you will have fun, it is simply a timeless game.", "appid": "6220", "steamid": "profiles/76561198426192465", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "27", "votes_funny": "3", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1589284800.0}
