{"text": "EDIT: For some reason I can't seem to be able to put my review under the Director's Cut version of this game so that the hours played would show correctly. The original version of this game I have only idled for 15 hours or so get the cards drop (which seemed to take forever by the way). In Director's Cut I have 210 hours, and this review is for the Director's Cut  . Maybe the best testimony I can give of Wasteland 2:Director's Cut is that it made me put in 210 hours in less than 6 weeks. Now I might have been a bit slow and thorough, but as you can tell by those hours the amount of content is huge. Maybe the first 20 hours or so I spent playing with my first crew which I then discarded, having learned enough of the mistakes I had made creating it. The rest of the time, 190 hours were divided between two complete playthroughs maybe by a ratio 100:90 respectively. It's not a flawless game and it may be easy to disagree on various amounts of it's design decisions. Nevertheless it certainly is a worthy effort in it's genre, and as a whole it captivated me like only a few percent of all games have done. If the post-apocalyptic theme appeals to you and/or you miss the classic isometric RPGs, I think you would be potentially denying yourself one heck of a ride by not giving this one at least a shot.", "appid": "240760", "steamid": "profiles/76561198034907165", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "31", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1460894400.0}
{"text": "This is the game that got me interested in VR and after spending over $450 on my oculus rift S and this game, I can definitely say that this game lives up to the hype. If you're debating purchasing this game on steam or another platform (oculus store) I'd definitely recommend purchasing it through steam as mods are the core to making this game more enjoyable than it already is. By mods I mostly mean custom songs as this allows for many many more hours of gameplay.", "appid": "620980", "steamid": "profiles/76561198368056667", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1596628800.0}
