{"text": "So I made the Campain and Play little bit of multiplayer. So Campain: Doom isn't story based game, they just had to put some in because the game would make no sense. You can customize weapons what is really cool. You can choose between 2 gadets and upgrade them for some kind of points or what. Lots of secrets, so be sure you chcek every room for HALO Master Chief action figure. I recommend playing this game on higher difficulities because I played on \"Hurt me plently\" (Normal) and I was bit bored I died maybe 20 times and 16 is because of â™¥â™¥â™¥â™¥â™¥ JUMPING! So, I enjoyed it much, buy it if you enjoy shooting a lot. And Multiplayer: Good old Quake with much overpowered demons and runes like quad damadge (I am saying like Quake) BUT, there is a leveling system and you can have only 2 weapons at time, then double jumping, you can equip gadet like classic granade or (excuse me) \"Personal Teleporter\" (that's really how it's called) but it's mine fauvorite. Back to demons. So they are just uno shot uno kill. You see him? Ha! You dead. But anyway those scrubs have no chance againts me old Quake king. I just destroyed them all. ALSO, there are spawning guns like Gauss Cannon which is freakin' OP AF BOIIIIIIIIIIII!!! It just gives you wallhacks when you aim downsights (or what it wants to be, basiclly when you hold right click) !!!!! So it's just Arena shooter. Again, no strategy just jump in and destroy everything. And also Snapmap: You make maps, you can publish them, you can play them and other players maps, just something that isn't typicall. It takes \"few\" hours to make a map so only for paitent people Also you can make those CO-OP. Verdict: +Nice atmosphere               +Good I don't know what just another plus               -I expected longer Campain but that doesn't matter               -JUMPING!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!                            -SPOILER ALLERT!!!!!!!!               -Did that motherf*cking shi*t butt robot sent me back to hell? I AM CONFUSED? Btw I was expecting last bossfight with him when he pull it up as sword but maybe next time.               -8.2/10 I don't make reviews often but maybe I am helpful.", "appid": "379720", "steamid": "profiles/76561198191703338", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1500724800.0}
