{"text": "Worms in 2D is back! In this game Team17 goes back to his roots. The game bring to you the classic 2D sideview jump 'n shoot fun game. I think it was a good decision to go back to 2D, even if I liked Worms Mayhem (which was the last Worms in 3D) a lot, it's quite the best solution if you like to play a fast game against friends. After 2min you have  assemble your own team if you didn't like to take a preassembled one. The controls are quite the same as in all the old Worms versions. Click the right mouse button to choose your weapon, aim with the arrow keys, and then hold the spacebar as long as you need, to determine the right amount of power. All the old weapons, as Bazooka, Grenade, Baseball bat, donkey etc. and even some new ones are aviable to bring you the full mass of destruction on your screen. If you liked one of the old 2D Worms game, I totallly recommend this game, and say this one is a \"Must have\".", "appid": "22600", "steamid": "profiles/76561197980081604", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1411560000.0}
