{"text": "This game is more of a relax, take a break from those other grindy games and just have fun type of game. I am about 2 hours in and enjoying it. The soundtrack is nice, the artwork unique and the game play a mix of deck building, light strategy and card battles. The enemies do get more difficult the higher challenges you unlock and you can play from an assortment of different dice characters with their own abilities and traits. I would recommend getting this game at sale price however as it is more of a time waster that a serious game you'd sink hours into. But you can replay levels many times as levels generate differently every time. Worth the sale price to experience a unique, fun game. Also I can see this game being fun for the young audience too!", "appid": "861540", "steamid": "profiles/76561198018894642", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1577534400.0}
