{"text": "Let me say at first that the game wasn't looking like +18 title based on trailer, more of a mystery drama. What I saw inside the game... Well without a doubt, these were hardcore h-scenes. What is your definition of fun? Hentai mixed with medieval torture horrors? Do you like sadism, besides everyday adultery with cute princesses? This game got you covered.  . Meanwhile story and proposed mystery... Story is just here because it can. It's not very developed neither concerning... it is the biggest fault here. I have nothing against gore scenes... but if the whole visual novel is about living in a prison with just a bit post mortem theatre, then we have a problem. Dialogues with Kloun are great he is mysterious leader of the whole scenery. Oh, and Marie on the other hand, she is certainly an idiot. I just can't even imagine how much empty her head must be. I can't feel into this game. It's just flat in so many places, and the way story is developing is like... rolling up an extension cord.  . The only fun of unknown is the next torture device... you cannot predict these at least. I am most certainly disappointed. There is nothing more than a just simple sadistic story, filled with hentai and torture h-scenes. The way this game looks and plays with words and voice acting was giving me a hope for something out-standing, but it's all for nothing. Here it's just hentai with mosaics.", "appid": "1357840", "steamid": "profiles/76561198009282696", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1605355200.0}
