{"text": "While the game is still fun to play after all these years, and looks better than ever, the humor goes past tounge in cheek to out right America bashing. No wonder this game was able to be remade. Its sense of humor can be boiled down to \"America sucks HUR DUR\". The Leftists who made this game even threw in a little history revisionism, having the soldiers brag about slaughtering Korean villages. What a disgusting insult to the memory of the brave men and women that died in that conflict protecting the Koreans from Chinese aggression! If you're looking for a repreive from the culture war, you won't find it here. Vote with your wallet. Again, the game play is solid enough for me to overlook the game's constant America bashing, but it does get old fast.", "appid": "803330", "steamid": "profiles/76561198009450953", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": "24", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1596110400.0}
