{"text": "While the game let you snipe its pretty fun, but some of the objectives you play more stealth than sniping so it becomes boring because there are better stealth games out there. Its not a bad game, but I`ll give you first mission as example. There are 50+ enemies, and 4 targets. So you can choose sneak around enemies or snipe most of them to clear your path to the targets. Since its a sniping game, I'll assume you want to snipe. Then to do it properly, without being detected and using sounds to mask your shots takes forever, because you shoot a guy. Then you wait like 3 minutes for another plane to mask the sound of the next shoot, well the target got behind a wall, cool 3 more minutes waiting for the next plane. And it's not just waiting, first target you can easily snipe. For the second and third at least I could not find a vatage point, so I did melee the second and the third was a meh snipe shot like 40mts shot just because I didnt want melee again. Best rating would be neutral, I would say get it on a sale with at least 30% off.", "appid": "312660", "steamid": "profiles/76561197967628966", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1493640000.0}
