{"text": "Well... I never expected the game to be great to start with, and got what I expected. It had some potential to be a mediocre    arcade boxing game but the controls completely killed it for me. They were unresponsive at the best of times and counter productive the rest of the time. Graphics and sound were what you'd expect from this level title. I heard the same comments from the annoucer multiple times in the few fights I fought. Every fight was the \"Fight of the decade\". Graphics are pretty bland and none of the fighters have much visual personality. Head graphics glitch multiple times per fight out of sync with the body as hits land.  Not a great title, might be worth it to waste an hour or two if you got it in a bundle. Otherwise pass.", "appid": "296770", "steamid": "profiles/76561197995933705", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "7", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1419508800.0}
