{"text": "Don't buy this because it's going free and leaving Steam to be an Epic exclusive. The game is really fun - when the matchmaking works. I've had a lot of great games and great teammates, but also a lot of horrible matchups. The game will put you on the losing side of a 0-4 or more game with 2 minutes left. What a terrible system. And when you're waiting for players for a new game, it'll give up after a few seconds and put bots on one or both teams. And if you're playing ranked, get ready for a ridiculous amount of quitters and flamers for a 5 minute game. A lot of the queues are pretty much empty, maybe that will improve eventually with F2P. Again, the game is really fun, especially with friends, but only when you're not fighting the matchmaking system or getting berated or frustrated because the game hasn't put you with players of similar skill.", "appid": "252950", "steamid": "profiles/76561198396723427", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1597060800.0}
