{"text": "I bought this game for my friend and I. We bought it during the winter sale when it was only five dollars, we would soon play with our other friends who also got this game. And I'll be frank with you, this game has always been on the worse side of the stick and now they're desperate so they made the game free we wasted our money. Since I didn't like the game as much I only played two hours and got refunded, and since my other friends played more then me they couldn't get refunded and it is simply evil. Do not get this game, they'll most likely do the same thing in the future. Steam will only refund if you have three hours or below that.", "appid": "433850", "steamid": "profiles/76561198314433544", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1521028800.0}
{"text": "Somewhere deep deep deep beneath theâ™¥â™¥â™¥â™¥â™¥â™¥is a good game.  Beneath the gamebreaking bugs, to the hilariously stupid ones. Beneath some of the worst AI in history Beneath combat that works 50% of the time 100% of the time. Beneath a plethora of half arsed side quests and hit or miss quest design. Beneath a lack of customisation and armors. Beneath the under developed perk system Beneath the awful stat bloat that makes the game a joke difficulty wise Beneath the most god awful pop in i have seen in a game for a while Beneath lack of diverse enemies and armors Beneath the missed opportunities when it comes to the life mechanics Beneath the most poorly designed lock on system in the history of gaming(seriously you dont need a lock on system) Beneath the lack of a feeling of progression character wise There is somewhere under all this, a decent game with some good mechanical systems and gameplay, and lots of untapped potential. I would have recommened this game (only just but i would have) had it not been for my feedback post being removed (it was literally this review) and called toxic by a forum mod.", "appid": "379430", "steamid": "profiles/76561198036457443", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "14", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1519041600.0}
