{"text": "This game is garbage. Legit pisses me off when i try to give it a chance. This game and its obsession with open world. the garbage that is locked behind the open world is ridiculous. I play to be the \"space ninja\" they advertise. Half the time you are spending is fishing and mining to get resources to craft â™¥â™¥â™¥â™¥. What is this minecraft? Dont get me started on the warframe ability immune bosses. Get this â™¥â™¥â™¥â™¥, DE gives us characters so we can use their abilities to be fancy. but when it comes to certain bosses, IMMUNE. Thats â™¥â™¥â™¥â™¥â™¥â™¥â™¥ dumb. It turns the game back into a generic â™¥â™¥â™¥â™¥â™¥â™¥ FPS like Call of duty. Whats the point of my abilities if i cant use them? I go to the open world to fish, minding my own business because i need \"standing\" for the â™¥â™¥â™¥â™¥â™¥â™¥ open world faction, then i suddenly get swarmed by enemies. Where in the name of god did they come from?! I'm legit by myself in the middle of nowhere and I'm getting bashed. The worst part is they target the fishies. THE â™¥â™¥â™¥â™¥â™¥â™¥â™¥ FISHIES DIED. See how this game tries to piss me off? Oh i almost forgot. The navigation system is complete aids. The devs still havent adjusted the markers when travelling. The markers have a mind of their own. Trying to piss you off whenever it gets the chance. You follow the marker to the ends of the earth, then it suddenly says go back. what is this garbage gps system. Waste of time. Save your time Trash end of story. Has good story tho", "appid": "230410", "steamid": "profiles/76561198027659835", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561982400.0}
