{"text": "Just paid $20 for stuff that should have been incorporated into the core game.  You know.. the one that ain't finished. FYI this one isn't finished either.  Devs these days are great at starting games but just can't finish one.   SE has less than half the dino variety and the terrain got boring fast. A free add-on at best. The age of the Alpha game.  We keep buyin it, they'll keep sellin stuff that'll never get finsihed, and I'm guilty. Never again, Wildcard.", "appid": "512540", "steamid": "profiles/76561198116819753", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "316", "votes_funny": "17", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1473249600.0}
